{"id": "art-201", "label": "Art. 201", "title": "Art. 201", "slug": "art-201", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 201 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_82766757\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1949\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_82766757\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Situa&#355;iile</span> financiare se\nîntocmesc potrivit normelor prev&#259;zute pentru societatea pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, prevederile art. 185 aplicându-se în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute pentru fondurile de rezerv&#259; la societatea pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, ca <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> acelea\nprivitoare la reducerea capitalului social, se aplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> cu r&#259;spundere\nlimitat&#259;.</span></p>"}